sentences: Nikolaj Koppel (born 6 March 1969 in Gentofte) is a Danish musician, journalist and radio presenter.
Nikolaj Koppel (born 6 March 1969 in Gentofte) is a Danish musician, journalist and radio presenter.
He studied at the Royal Danish Academy of Music and went on to become a concert pianist in 1998, but retired from the business after just two years.
